2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHumans%20use%20coding%20languages%20to%20communicate%20with%20computers%20by%20providing%20a%20set%20of%20instructions%20for%20a%20system%20to%20execute.%20%3Cspan%3EMany%20kinds%20of%20coding%20languages%20are%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftop-coding-languages-for-wall-street-jobs-banks-hedge-funds-2022-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eused%20on%20Wall%20Street%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20from%20more%20general-purpose%20languages%20like%20Python%20and%20Java%20to%20more%20specialized%20ones%20like%20SQL%2C%20which%20are%20used%20heavily%20when%20working%20with%20data%20and%20databases.%20If%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcareer-change-designing-video-games-finance-citadel-riot-games-microsoft-2022-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ea%20company%20needs%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcareer-change-designing-video-games-finance-citadel-riot-games-microsoft-2022-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Espeed%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20there's%20a%20good%20chance%20you'll%20find%20C%2B%2B.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EC%2B%2B%20is%20often%20used%20at%20high-frequency%20trading%20firms%20and%20exchanges%2C%20where%20companies%20gain%20an%20edge%20by%20being%20microseconds%20faster%20than%20the%20competition.%20It's%20known%20as%20a%20low-level%20language%20that%20gives%20engineers%20more%20control%20over%20how%20systems%20work%20under%20the%20hood.%20But%20with%20that%20control%20comes%20more%20complexity%20and%20opportunities%20for%20nasty%20problems.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EC%2B%2B%20coders%20have%20more%20control%20over%20computer%20hardware%20and%20memory.%20This%20level%20of%20control%20is%20similar%20to%20how%20drivers%20of%20manual%20cars%20can%20adjust%20engine%20settings%20and%20time%20when%20they%20shift%20gears%20for%20maximum%20performance%20versus%20automatic-car%20drivers%20who%20don't%20have%20to%20worry%20about%20operating%20the%20clutch%20or%20messing%20with%20the%20gears.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJust%20like%20manual%20drivers%20can%20stall%20out%20if%20the%20clutch%2C%20gas%20pedal%2C%20and%20gear%20shifter%20don't%20work%20in%20unison%2C%20having%20that%20low-level%20control%20between%20hardware%20and%20software%20can%20lead%20to%20thorny%20issues%20that%20aren't%20always%20straightforward%20to%20resolve.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20C%2B%2B%20has%20been%20around%20for%20decades%2C%20it's%20constantly%20being%20evolved%20and%20adapted%20to%20make%20it%20more%20powerful%20and%20accessible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BC%2B%2B%20is%20critically%20important%20to%20our%20business%20and%20the%20capital%20markets%2C%20and%20I'm%20excited%20by%20the%20opportunity%20for%20us%20to%20work%20with%20Herb%20and%20the%20C%2B%2B%20community%20to%20continue%20to%20evolve%20the%20language%2C%20particularly%20in%20the%20areas%20of%20ease%20of%20use%20and%20safety%2C%26quot%3B%20Woods%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-citadel-securities-hired-coding-expert-microsoft-herb-sutter-2024-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731322201000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F672e5775192f525898570a33%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-citadel-securities-hired-coding-expert-microsoft-herb-sutter-2024-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Herb%20Sutter%20is%20a%20leading%20expert%20in%20C%2B%2B%2C%20a%20critical%20coding%20language%20for%20the%20giant%20market%20maker.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Bianca%20Chan)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A11%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-citadel-securities-hired-coding-expert-microsoft-herb-sutter-2024-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BCompletely%20False%26quot%3B%3A%20Kremlin%20Denies%20Putin%2C%20Trump%20Spoke%20Over%20Phone%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ECalling%20it%20%26quot%3Bcompletely%20false%26quot%3B%2C%20Moscow%20today%20rejected%20claims%20of%20a%20phone%20call%20between%20Vladimir%20Putin%20and%20Donald%20Trump%20last%20week.%20A%20report%20by%20US's%20Washington%20Post%20had%20claimed%20on%20Sunday%20that%20Trump%20had%20called%20up%20Putin%2C%20and%20that%20the%20two%20leaders%20had%20discussed%20the%20conflict%20in%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20completely%20false%20information%2C%26quot%3B%20Kremlin%20spokesperson%20Dmitry%20Peskov%20said%20today%2C%20adding%20that%20there%20has%20been%20no%20phone%20call%20whatsoever%2C%20between%20the%20Russian%20President%20and%20his%20US%20counterpart.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20report%2C%20now%20flagged%20as%20'fake%20news'%20by%20Moscow%2C%20The%20Washington%20Post%20had%20claimed%20that%20Donald%20Trump%20had%20called%20Vladimir%20Putin%20from%20his%20residence-cum-resort%20Mar-a-Lago%20in%20Palm%20Beach%2C%20Florida.%20The%20call%20was%20reportedly%20made%20on%20Thursday%2C%20a%20day%20after%20Trump%20and%20his%20close%20aide%20Elon%20Musk%20had%20spoken%20to%20Ukraine's%20Zelensky.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Washington%20Post%20report%2C%20which%20was%20based%20on%20'anonymous%20sources%20familiar%20with%20the%20matter'%2C%20Trump%20had%20allegedly%20%26quot%3Breminded%20Putin%26quot%3B%20of%20America's%20sizable%20military%20presence%20in%20Europe.%20The%20report%20went%20on%20to%20claim%20that%20Trump%20had%20allegedly%20expressed%20an%20interest%20in%20further%20conversations%20with%20Putin%20to%20discuss%20%26quot%3Bthe%20resolution%20of%20Ukraine's%20war%20soon.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EDONALD%20TRUMP%20CALLS%20UKRAINE'S%20ZELENSKY%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20in%20his%20victory%20speech%20after%20the%202024%20US%20Election%20result%20was%20declared%20last%20week%2C%20Donald%20Trump%20had%20said%20that%20%26quot%3BI%20will%20not%20start%20wars%2C%20I%20will%20help%20end%20them%26quot%3B%2C%20and%20within%20a%20few%20days%20of%20winning%20the%20presidential%20election%2C%20President-elect%20Trump%20had%20called%20his%20Ukrainian%20counterpart%20Zelensky.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20phone%20call%20last%20Wednesday%2C%20President%20Zelensky%20had%20shared%20a%20post%20on%20X%20which%20read%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20had%20an%20excellent%20call%20with%20President%20Trump%20and%20congratulated%20him%20on%20his%20historic%20landslide%20victory%20-%20his%20tremendous%20campaign%20made%20this%20result%20possible.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fcl3gesag_trump-musk_625x300_13_August_24.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20that%20phone%20call%20was%20attended%20by%20Elon%20Musk%20too.%20Elon%20Musk%20was%20with%20Donald%20Trump%20at%20the%20President-elect's%20residence%20and%20luxury%20resort%20Mar-a-Lago.%20During%20the%20phone%20call%2C%20Donald%20Trump%20reportedly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdonald-trump-asks-elon-musk-to-join-call-with-ukraines-zelensky-in-big-hint-at-his-possible-role-6976601%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehanded%20the%20phone%20over%20to%20Elon%20Musk%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20supposedly%20asked%20the%20SpaceX%20founder%20to%20join%20the%20call%20with%20President%20Zelensky.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20not%20known%20yet%2C%20if%20they%20discussed%20any%20change%20in%20policy%20the%20United%20States%20has%20towards%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20news%20report%20by%20Axios%2C%20there%20were%20two%20surprises%20that%20day%20-%20the%20first%20being%20that%20Elon%20Musk%20spoke%20with%20Zelensky%2C%20and%20the%20second%2C%20that%20Zelensky%20wa