rget%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHack%20Your%20HR%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202023%2C%20where%20I%20create%20short-form%20content%20in%20the%20HR%20space.%20In%20my%20Instagram%20videos%2C%20I%20share%20advice%20to%20help%20people%20get%20ahead%20in%20their%20corporate%20jobs%20and%20information%20about%20the%20back%20end%20of%20HR.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20help%20people%20understand%20how%20to%20advocate%20for%20themselves%20at%20work%2C%20what%20language%20to%20use%20with%20their%20managers%2C%20and%20how%20to%20ask%20for%20help%20if%20they're%20not%20getting%20the%20support%20they%20need.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20HR%20can%20help%20with%20a%20lot%2C%20they%20can't%20fix%20every%20problem%20you%20may%20have%20as%20an%20employee.%20Here%20are%20three%20things%20you're%20wasting%20your%20time%20on%20if%20you%20take%20them%20to%20HR.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2242d9c325-db7e-4c68-a2d0-fc6350e149fd%5C%22%3E1.%20HR%20can't%20make%20decisions%20alone%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEvery%20HR%20department%20is%20run%20differently%2C%20so%20while%20HR%20tasks%20may%20vary%2C%20HR%20isn't%20typically%20a%20decision-making%20entity%20but%20more%20of%20a%20recommending%20entity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20someone%20wants%20a%20promotion%20and%20their%20manager%20says%20no%2C%20they%20might%20go%20to%20HR%2C%20thinking%2C%20%26quot%3BI'm%20going%20to%20appeal%20to%20HR%2C%20and%20then%20%3Cem%3Ethey%3C%2Fem%3E%20will%20be%20able%20to%20decide%20if%20I%20get%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20like%20saying%20if%20I%20go%20to%20Mom%20and%20she%20doesn't%20give%20me%20what%20I%20want%2C%20I%20will%20go%20to%20Dad.%20It%20doesn't%20work%20like%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20it%20can%20sometimes%20be%20misperceived%20that%20HR%20approves%20salaries.%20Typically%2C%20HR%20is%20the%20messenger%20for%20budgets%2C%20not%20the%20one%20deciding.%20We%20might%20recommend%20a%20number%20based%20on%20what's%20legal%2C%20compliant%2C%20and%20makes%20sense%20within%20compensation%20guardrails%2C%20but%20ulti