20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%20GM%20said%20it%20has%20doubled%20its%20staff%20in%20Silicon%20Valley%20over%20the%20past%20six%20months%20and%20is%20competitive%20in%20hiring%20talent%20away%20from%20tech%20firms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENine%20current%20and%20former%20people%20in%20engineering%20and%20sales%20said%20that%20Tesla's%20stock%20grants%20make%20it%20easier%20to%20accept%20lower%20base%20salaries.%20Tesla%20stock%20could%20make%20them%20rich%2C%20if%20only%20on%20paper.%20On%20November%208%2C%20the%20automaker's%20stock%20surged%20more%208%25%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20Donald%20Trump's%20re-election%2C%20hitting%20a%20market%20cap%20of%20%241%20trillion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20Tesla%20employees%20can%20receive%20millions%20of%20dollars%20in%20stock.%20In%202020%20and%202021%2C%2044%20US-based%20employees%20were%20offered%20stock%20worth%20more%20than%20%241%20million%2C%20according%20to%20the%20database.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20get%20a%20sense%20of%20which%20employees%20were%20more%20likely%20to%20take%20home%20large%20grants%2C%20BI%20broke%20up%20stock%20grants%20based%20on%20job%20category.%20The%20data%20show%20that%20most%20workers%20in%20engineering%20received%20stock%20grants%20above%20%2425%2C000.%20The%20value%20of%20the%20stock%20is%20based%20on%20the%20value%20of%20the%20shares%20at%20the%20time%20they%20were%20granted%2C%20but%20it's%20subject%20to%20change%20based%20on%20Tesla's%20share%20price.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20the%20stock%20offerings%20at%20Tesla%2C%20about%2075%25%20were%20restricted%20stock%20units%2C%20or%20RSUs%2C%20while%20nonqualified%20stock%20options%20made%20up%2021%25%2C%20and%20were%20given%20exclusively%20as%20merit-based%20compensation%2C%20according%20to%20BI's%20analysis%20of%20US-based%2C%20full-time%20workers.%20Only%204%25%20of%20employees%20%E2%80%94%20including%20many%20executives%20and%20other%20high-level%20workers%20%E2%80%94%20received%20the%20stock%20as%20incentive%20stock%20options%2C%20or%20ISOs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZaheer%20Mohiuddin%2C%20the%20cofounder%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2FLevels.fyi%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELevels.fyi%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20said%20RSUs%20are%20very%20common%20in%20tech%2C%20while%20incentive%20stock%20options%20are%20typically%20reserved%20for%20longtime%20high-level%20employees%20or%20nonpublic%20companies.%20RSUs%20are%20typically%20included%20in%20standard%20compensation%20packages%2C%20while%20nonqualified%20stock%20options%20and%20ISOs%20are%20often%20used%20as%20additional%20incentives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERSUs%20give%20employees%20actual%20shares%20that%20vest%20over%20time%2C%20while%20ISOs%20simply%20provide%20the%20right%20to%20purchase%20stock%20at%20a%20preset%20price%20before%20expiration%20%E2%80%94%20which%20is%20potentially%20profitable%20if%20the%20stock%20price%20rises%20above%20that%20level%2C%20but%20also%20requires%20the%20employee%20to%20have%20money%20on%20hand%20to%20pay%20for%20the%20stock%20in%20the%20first%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftbimedia.s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com%2Fbistudios%2F_00%2Fdev_edit%2Fgraphics%2F2024%2F10%2F2024-10-teslacomp-stockgrants%2Findex.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22breakout-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cfigure%20data-chart%3D%5C%22ai2html%5C%22%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EOutside%20of%20one%20person%20within%20Tesla's%20executive%20job%20category%20who%20had%20no%20stock%20amount%20listed%2C%20Tesla%20executives%20received%20stock%20offerings%20worth%20between%20%24950%2C000%20and%20%2420%20million%2C%20according%20to%20the%20database%2C%20which%20displayed%20the%20latest%20stock%20amount%20for%20each%20employee%20as%20of%20December%202021.%20All%20but%20one%20of%20the%20executives'%20offerings%20were%20ISOs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETesla%20is%20far%20from%20the%20first%20company%20to%20enhance%20base%20pay%20with%20stock%20grants.%20Companies%20like%20Meta%2C%20Google%2C%20and%20Amazon%20have%20been%20known%20to%20offer%20employees%20healthy%20stock%20grants.%20Employee%20survey%20data%20from%202024%20from%20the%20compensation-benchmarking%20company%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2FLevels.fyi%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELevels.fyi%3C%2Fa%3E%20found%20that%20Tesla's%20median%20base%20pay%20and%20stock%20grants%20for%20US-based%20software%20engineers%20are%20slightly%20lower%20than%20that%20of%20US-based%20software%20engineers%20at%20Meta%2C%20Amazon%2C%20Apple%2C%20Netflix%2C%20and%20Alphabet%2C%20collectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20five%20years%2C%20Tesla's%20stock%20has%20spiked%20well%20over%201%2C000%25%3B%20that%20performance%20potentially%20makes%20those%20grants%20attractive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGreg%20Selker%2C%20a%20managing%20director%20at%20the%20executive%20recruitment%20firm%20Stanton%20Chase%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20while%20other%20Big%20Tech%20companies%20might%20have%20higher%20base%20pay%20and%20equity%20grants%20to%20match%2C%20Tesla's%20strength%20also%20lies%20in%20its%20image.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20mission-driven%20element%20to%20it%20that%20allows%20Tesla%20to%20get%20away%20with%20paying%20less%2C%26quot%3B%20Selker%20said.%20%26quot%3BThese%20people%20are%20working%20to%20bring%20about%20the%20decarbonization%20of%20the%20planet.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20has%20previously%20described%20what%20the%20stock%20options%20can%20do%20for%20employees.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%26quot%3BWe%20give%20everyone%20stock%20options%3B%20we've%20made%20many%20people%20who%20are%20just%20working%20the%20line%20%E2%80%94%20who%20didn't%20even%20know%20what%20stocks%20were%20%E2%80%94%20we've%20made%20them%20millionaires%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffortune.com%2F2023%2F11%2F30%2Ftesla-elon-mus-unionize-staff-millionaires-stock-options%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBI%20examined%20the%20median%20stock%20grants%20and%20the%20percentage%20of%20employees%20who%20received%20grants%20for%20each%20job%20category%20and%20found%20that%20a%20majority%20of%20workers%20in%20nearly%20every%20category%20received%20some%20type%20of%20stock%20grant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2Fpuisf%2F1%2F%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Tesla%20stock%20grants%20by%20job%20family%5C%22%20data-external%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22654%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3ETesla's%20pay%20strategy%20has%20more%20in%20common%20with%20other%20Silicon%20Valley%20companies%20like%20Google%20or%20Meta%20than%20it%20does%20with%20traditional%20automakers%2C%20Harley%20Shaiken%2C%20an%20auto%20industry%20and%20labor%20expert%2C%20told%20BI.%20Traditional%20automakers%20like%20GM%20or%20Ford%20rely%20on%20higher%20base%20pay%20while%20companies%20like%20Tesla%2C%20which%20has%20seen%20higher%20stock%20returns%20over%20the%20past%20five%20years%2C%20can%20attract%20talent%20through%20stock%20grants%2C%20Shaiken%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTech%20workers%20are%20looking%20for%20the%20opportunity%20for%20a%20big%20payday%2C%20not%20just%20an%20incremental%20salary%20bump%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20former%20sales%20manager%20said%20Tesla's%20stock%20offerings%20initially%20attracted%20him%20to%20the%20role%2C%20but%20he%20compared%20them%20to%20%26quot%3Bgolden%20handcuffs.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20stock%20is%20the%20major%20hook.%20You%20might%20be%20unhappy%20in%20your%20role%2C%20but%20you%20just%20decide%2C%20'I'm%20going%20to%20keep%20my%20head%20down%20and%20wait%20a%20few%20months%20longer%20until%20I%20vest%2C'%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETesla's%20stock%20offerings%20have%20given%20some%20workers%20opportunities%20for%20major%20paydays.%20Drew%20Baglino%2C%20Tesla's%20former%20senior%20vice%20president%20of%20powertrain%20and%20energy%20engineering%2C%20and%20Zachary%20Kirkhorn%2C%20the%20former%20CFO%2C%20were%20awarded%20%2420%20million%20each.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20executives%2C%20including%20Musk's%20right-hand%20man%20Omead%20Afshar%2C%20received%20%2410%20million%20in%20stock%20offerings%2C%20according%20to%20the%20database.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20part%20of%20the%20benefit%20of%20taking%20a%20chance%20on%20a%20company%20like%20Tesla%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20engineer%20who%20joined%20the%20company%20in%202015%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BYou%20might%20have%20to%20deal%20with%20the%20aches%20and%20pains%20of%20a%20startup%20%E2%80%94%20the%20long%20hours%2C%20some%20of%20the%20uncertainty%20%E2%80%94%20but%20there%20can%20also%20be%20a%20significant%20payoff.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAaron%20Greenspan%2C%20a%20vocal%20critic%20of%20Musk%20and%20the%20founder%20of%20PlainSite%2C%20an%20organization%20that%20provides%20access%20to%20legal%20documents%20and%20advocates%20for%20legal%20transparency%2C%20first%20referenced%20Afshar's%20stock%20grant%20in%20a%20lawsuit%20filed%20against%20defendants%20including%20Musk%20and%20Tesla%2C%20accusing%20them%20of%20defamation%2C%20among%20other%20claims.%20Lawyers%20for%20Musk%20and%20Tesla%20have%20called%20his%20claims%20%26quot%3Blargely%20unintelligible%20allegations.%26quot%3B%20The%20lawsuit%20is%20ongoing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETesla%20awards%20stock%20grants%20with%20promotions%20and%20annual%20reviews%20and%20bases%20them%20on%20the%20company's%20performance%2C%20according%20to%20the%20salary%20database%20and%20conversations%20with%20four%20current%20employees.%20Last%20year%2C%20the%20company%20cut%20back%20on%20merit-based%20stock%20awards%20for%20staff%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2023-12-19%2Ftesla-skips-merit-based-stock-awards-squeezing-compensation%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBloomberg%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20four%20employees%20told%20BI.%20In%20June%2C%20Musk%20told%20staff%20he%20planned%20to%20award%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-stock-option-grants-awards-elon-musk-email-2024-6%23%3A~%3Atext%3DTesla%2520will%2520reward%2520employees%2520for%2Cat%2520Tesla%2520earlier%2520this%2520year.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eadditional%20stock%20grants%20for%20%26quot%3Bexceptional%20performance.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20During%20annual%20performance%20reviews%20in%20July%2C%20managers%20were%20limited%20to%20recommending%20no%20more%20than%2020%25%20of%20their%20team%20to%20be%20considered%20for%20the%20extra%20award%2C%20two%20people%20with%20knowledge%20said.%20Tesla%20typically%20awards%20employees%20restricted%20stock%20units%20that%20vest%20over%20a%20period%20of%20four%20years%2C%20the%20data%20show.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESelker%20said%20historically%20Tesla%20workers%20have%20been%20able%20to%20count%20on%20their%20stock%20continuing%20to%20grow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20bet%20they%20have%20to%20make%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20So%20far%2C%20stock%20grants%20have%20%26quot%3Bproven%20to%20be%20better%20than%20cash%20in%20your%20pocket.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%2C%20if%20the%20stock%20were%20to%20become%20inconsistent%20or%20halve%2C%20then%20Tesla%20will%20have%20to%20change%20its%20strategy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETesla's%20stock%20has%20experienced%20significant%20volatility%20this%20year%2C%20slumping%20as%20low%20as%2044%25%20in%20mid-April%20from%20its%20price%20at%20the%20start%20of%20the%20year.%20Following%20Donald%20Trump's%20re-election%2C%20it's%20up%20nearly%2030%25%20overall%20year%20to%20date.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20least%20one%20longtime%20Tesla%20staffer%20worries%20about%20new%20hires.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20feel%20lucky%20that%20I%20got%20in%20early%2C%20but%20I%20see%20a%20lot%20of%20younger%20engineers%20expecting%20to%20reap%20the%20same%20benefits%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20s