r%20daily%20trauma%3B%20he%20tried%20to%20push%20a%20coal-laden%20bicycle%20-%20carrying%20a%20back-breaking%20200%20kg%20-%20and%20called%20for%20justice%2C%20that%20these%20men%20be%20paid%20better%20for%20their%20hard%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYet%2C%20despite%20that%20headline%20and%20the%20Congress%20being%20part%20of%20the%20ruling%20alliance%20in%20Jharkhand%2C%20the%20lives%20of%20these%20'cycle%20coal%20workers'%20remains%20unchanged%20and%20as%20difficult%20as%20ever.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%2C%20alongside%20them%20stumble%20along%20men%20charging%20Rs%20100%20to%20help%20push%20these%20coal-laden%20bicycles%20uphill%2C%20adding%20to%20a%20complex%20ecosystem%20of%20survival%20the%20only%20goal%20of%20which%20is%20survival.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20one%20and%20all%20they%20lament%20'missing%20in%20action'%20MLAs%20and%20lawmakers%2C%20who%20%26quot%3Bpromise%20employment%20during%20elections%20but%2C%20after%20winning%2C%20disappear%26quot%3B.%20Yet%2C%20they%20say%2C%20each%20election%20they%20vote%20because%20%26quot%3Bthat%20is%20all%20we%20have...%20a%20flickering%20hope...%20perhaps%20false...%20but%20hope%20nonetheless.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EMathura%20Ravidas%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20name%20is%20Mathura%20Ravidas.%20I%20live%20in%20Asurbandh%20in%20Bokaro.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERavidas%20loads%20his%20bicycle%20with%20around%20240%20kg%20of%20coal%20every%20day.%20He%20buys%20this%20for%20Rs%20650%20and%20sells%20it%20for%20Rs%20900.%20%26quot%3BThe%20profit%20isn't%20much%20but%20it%20is%20enough%20to%20keep%20us%20going%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERavidas%20has%20six%20children%20and%20he%20is%20the%20sole%20earner%20in%20the%20family%2C%20and%20where%20he%20lives%20there%20is%2C%20he%20said%2C%20no%20other%20job%20or%20source%20of%20income.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20journey%20back%20(with%20coal)%20is%20gruelling...%20sometimes%20the%20climb%20is%20so%20steep%20and%20the%20load%20so%20heavy%20I%20stumble%20and%20fall%2C%20and%20get%20hurt.%20It%20takes%20six%20or%20seven%20hours%20just%20to%20return%20home.%20I%20wonder%20if%20there%20will%20ever%20be%20a%20better%20life%20for%20my%20children%2C%20one%20in%20which%20they%20don't%20have%20to%20carry%20this%20weight.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22jharkhand%20coal%20workers%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22jharkhand%20coal%20workers%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fmjf0ii4o_jharkhand-coal-workers_625x300_11_November_24.jpeg%3Fim%3DFitAndFill%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3Ejharkhand%20coal%20workers%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20know%20who%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20is...%20the%20leader%20who%20came%20and%20tried%20to%20push%20a%20coal-laden%20bicycle%20like%20ours.%20It%20is%20nice%20someone%20noticed...%20but%20we%20are%20still%20waiting%20for%20real%20change.%20Every%20day%20we%20risk%20our%20lives%2C%20hoping%20someday%20the%20pain%20of%20carrying%20this%20load%20will%20subside%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EMunna%20Yadav%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20Munna%20Yadav.%20Today%2C%20I%20left%20Giridih%20at%202%20am%20and%20reached%20Chhotki%20Khargadiha%20(a%20distance%20of%20around%2025%20km)%20to%20sell%20my%20coal.%20My%20cycle%20carried%2015%20baskets%20-%20around%20300%20kg.%20I%20buy%20each%20for%20Rs%20120%20and%20sell%20it%20for%20Rs%20220.%20I%20have%20eight%20family%20members%2C%20and%20earn%20Rs%20500-600%20per%20trip.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20has%20been%20my%20life%20for%20the%20past%2020%20years%20but%2C%20as%20I%20get%20older%2C%20it%20becomes%20harder.%20I%20wake%20up%20in%20the%20darkness%20of%20night%2C%20bearing%20this%20weight.%20Every%20election%20I%20think...%20maybe%20this%20time%2C%20the%20MLA%20will%20keep%20their%20word%20and%20give%20us%20an%20opportunity%20to%20leave%20this%20work%20behind...%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYadav%20told%20NDTV%20there%20are%20100%20to%20150%20people%20in%20his%20village%20who%20do%20this%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20we%20are%20sick%2C%20we%20have%20to%20go%20to%20the%20hospital%20in%20Bengabad%20as%20we%20have%20no%20healthcare%20nearby.%20I%20dream%20of%20a%20life%20without%20this%20burden...%20my%20children%20can%20have%20better%20opportunities.%20Whoever%20forms%20the%20government%2C%20I%20hope%20they%20listen%20to%20us%20and%20offer%20real%20work.%20Until%20then%2C%20we%20will%20carry%20this%20weight.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Invisible%20But%20Essential%20Workforce%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Jharkhand%2C%20coal%20represents%20survival%20and%20hardship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJharkhand%20holds%20nearly%2040%20per%20cent%20of%20India's%20mineral%20wealth%2C%20including%2027.3%20per%20cent%20of%20its%20coal%20reserves%2C%20making%20it%20the%20country's%20largest%20coal-producing%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20November%202022%20the%20state%20government%20set%20up%20a%20Just%20Transition%20Task%20Force%20to%20address%20the%20needs%20of%20coal-dependent%20regions%20and%20transition%20to%20more%20sustainable%20livelihoods.%20Yet%2C%20despite%20this%20initiative%2C%20workers%20like%20Ravidas%20and%20Yadav%20remain%20invisible.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731315780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fmn8q8goo_jharkhand-coal-workers_625x300_11_November_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Finvisible-burden-jharkhands-cycle-coal-workers-and-weight-of-survival-6992681%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22For%20coal%20mine%20workers%20in%20Jharkhand%2C%20each%20election%20offers%20a%20measure%20of%20hope%20to%20improve%20their%20miserable%20social%20and%20economic%20fortunes%20but%20each%2C%20ultimately%2C%20dissolves%20into%20nothingness%2C%20each%20day%20filled%20with%20long%20hours%20of%20toil%20buried%20underground.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Finvisible-burden-jharkhands-cycle-coal-workers-and-weight-of-survival-6992681%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20India%20Or%20Canada%3A%20Which%20Way%20Will%20Trump%20Look%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2F7lgvhhno_trump_625x300_11_November_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt's%20no%20surprise%20that%20many%20Indians%E2%80%94including%20some%20former%20diplomats%E2%80%94are%20celebrating%20Donald%20Trump's%20reelection.%20After%20all%2C%20Trump's%20bond%20with%20India%2C%20and%20particularly%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20was%20the%20envy%20of%20many%20countries%20and%20leaders%20during%20his%20first%20term.%20Granted%2C%20some%20might%20say%20they%20were%20mere%20optics%3A%20remember%20appearances%20at%20rallies%20like%20%E2%80%9CHowdy%2C%20Modi!%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9CNamaste%2C%20Trump!%E2%80%9D%20in%20Houston%20and%20Ahmedabad%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20Trump's%20return%20to%20the%20Oval%20Office%20just%20weeks%20away%2C%20some%20in%20India%20are%20already%20hoping%20that%20he%20will%20put%20New%20Delhi's%20new%20adversary%2C%20Canadian%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau%2C%20in%20his%20place.%20After%20all%2C%20Trump's%20past%20comments%20on%20Trudeau%20range%20from%20%E2%80%9Cweak%E2%80%9D%20to%20%E2%80%9Ctwo-faced%26quot%3B%2C%20to%20even%20%E2%80%9Cfar-left%20lunatic%E2%80%9D%E2%80%94hardly%20a%20subtle%20hint%20of%20his%20opinion%20of%20his%20neighbouring%20country's%20leader.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20Canadians%20Are%20Worried%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Canadians%2C%20though%2C%20Trump's%20second%20term%20has%20sparked%20more%20shock%20than%20celebration.%20Deputy%20Prime%20Minister%20Chrystia%20Freeland%20(also%20the%20country's%20finance%20minister)%20held%20two%20press%20conferences%20post%20his%20election%20to%20calm%20Canadian%20nerves%2C%20saying%20Canada%20will%20be%20%E2%80%9Cabsolutely%20fine%E2%80%9D.%20Yet%2C%20many%20Canadians%20remain%20uneasy%20over%20Trump's%20return%20to%20the%20White%20House%2C%20and%20for%20good%20reason.%20There%20are%20three%20big%20areas%20of%20anxiety%3A%20tariffs%2C%20NATO%20contributions%20and%20the%20looming%20renegotiation%20of%20the%20US-Mexico-Canada%20Agreement%20(USMCA).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20Trump%20has%20hinted%20at%20slapping%20a%20blanket%2010%25%20tariff%20on%20all%20imports%20to%20the%20US%2C%20which%20would%20hit%20Canada%20hard%20given%20that%20more%20than%20two-thirds%20of%20its%20exports%20are%20US-bound.%20Then%20there%20is%20Trump's%20expectation%20that%20NATO%20members%20chip%20in%20a%20full%202%25%20of%20their%20GDP%20on%20defence.%20Canada%20is%20currently%20far%20behind%20and%20contributing%20only%201.23%25%E2%80%94a%20potential%20sticking%20point%20if%20Trump%20insists%20on%20the%20required%20contributions%20like%20he%20did%20during%20the%20last%20term.%20Lastly%2C%20there's%20the%20USMCA%2C%20which%20Trump%20himself%20strong-armed%20Canada%20and%20Mexico%20into%20renegotiating%20in%202020.%20Trump%20has%20hinted%20that%20the%20deal%20is%20set%20for%20review%20in%202026.%20Canadians%20worry%20that%20the%20President-elect%20could%20push%20for%20even%20stricter%20terms%20this%20time%20around.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWill%20Trump%20Side%20With%20India%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiden's%20team%20and%20its%20Western%20European%20pals%20are%20clearly%20frustrated%20with%20India's%20refusal%20to%20oppose%20Russia%20over%20the%20Ukraine%20war.%20They%20have%20not%20said%20it%20out%20loud%2C%20but%20it's%20hard%20not%20to%20suspect%20that%20they%20are%20quietly%20backing%20Trudeau%20behind%20the%20scenes%20in%20his%20finger-pointing%20at%20India%2C%20accusing%20officials%20of%20involvement%20in%20the%20killing%20of%20Sikh%20separatist%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar.%20Let's%20be%20real%E2%80%94it%20wasn't%20without%20Big%20Brother's%20nod%20that%20Trudeau%20stood%20in%20Parliament%20last%20year%20hurling%20accusations%20at%20India.%20Furthermore%2C%20if%20Canada%20decides%20to%20move%20forward%20with%20these%20allegations%2C%20the%20possibility%20is%20it%20won't%20be%20acting%20alone.%20The%20US%20and%20the%20UK%2C%20key%20members%20of%20the%20Five%20Eyes%20alliance%2C%20have%20often%20helped%20manage%20diplomatic%20and%20security%20issues%20with%20countries%20outside%20the%20alliance.%20Since%20both%20countries%20have%20close%20ties%20with%20India%2C%20they%20may%20help%20Canada%20weigh%20the%20strength%20and%20possible%20impact%20of%20these%20accusations%20before%20taking%20any%20official%20steps.%20Still%2C%20accusing%20a%20powerful%20country%20like%20India%20could%20affect%20important%20strategic%20interests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20the%20possible%20egging%20on%20by%20Big%20Brother%20suits%20Trudeau%20too%2C%20giving%20him%20a%20shot%20at%20placating%20his%20Sikh%20voter%20base%20and%20propping%20up%20his%20waning%20popularity.%20However%2C%20only%20a%20rookie%20diplomat%2C%20I%20would%20say%2C%20can%20fully%20trust%20the%20self-serving%20strategy%20that%20the%20US%20usually%20follows.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20cannot%20underplay%20US%20State%20Department%20spokesman%20Matthew%20Miller's%20blunt%20statement%20last%20month%3A%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20the%20Canadian%20matter%2C%20we%20have%20made%20clear%20that%20the%20allegations%20are%20extremely%20serious%20and%20they%20need%20to%20be%20taken%20seriously.%20We%20wanted%20to%20see%20the%20government%20of%20India%20cooperate%20with%20Canada%20in%20its%20investigation.%20Obviously%2C%20they%20have%20not%20chosen%20that%20path.%E2%80%9D%20%C2%A0The%20statement%20did%20not%20reflect%20India's%20position%20that%20there%20was%20complete%20disregard%20for%20New%20Delhi's%20request%20to%20Ottawa%20to%20share%20evidence.%20And%20now%2C%20with%20allegations%20of%20India's%20involvement%20in%20an%20attempted%20assassination%2C%20the%20Biden%20administration%20has%20another%20card%20to%20play.%20Nonetheless%2C%20India%20is%20cooperating%20with%20the%20US%20on%20the%20investigation%20and%20neither%20side%20wants%20to%20blow%20it%20out%20of%20proportion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20as%20Trump%20re-enters%20his%20office%2C%20his%20promise%20to%20end%20the%20war%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20if%20fulfilled%2C%20will%20be%20a%20game-changer.%20Without%20Ukraine%20in%20the%20equation%2C%20the%20US%20pressure%20on%20India%20to%20pick%20a%20side%20goes%20out%20of%20the%20window%2C%20and%20Biden's%20%E2%80%9Ccold-shoulder%E2%80%9D%20tactics%20would%20become%20a%20non-issue.%20Trump%2C%20however%2C%20we%20all%20know%2C%20is%20a%20wildcard.%20While%20he%20may%20want%20closer%20ties%20with%20India%2C%20we%20know%20how%20that%20%E2%80%9CAmerica%20First%E2%80%9D%20agenda%20translates%3A%20tariffs%2C%20immigration%20restrictions%20and%20a%20hard%20line%20on%20H-1B%20visas.%20Fortunately%20though%2C%20Trump's%20stance%20on%20Russia%20(to%20end%20the%20war)%20aligns%20with%20India's%2C%20as%20does%20his%20anti-China%20focus.%20It's%20quite%20possible%20he%20might%20ask%20Trudeau%20to%20either%20produce%20proof%20in%20the%20Nijjar%20case%20or%20drop%20the%20offensive.%20Who%20knows.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EBut%20Don't%20Underestimate%20US-Canada%20Bond%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20so%2C%20we%20should%20never%20underestimate%20America's%20deep-rooted%20ties%20with%20Canada%E2%80%94they%20are%20in%20a%20league%20of%20their%20own.%20Sure%2C%20Trump%20and%20Trudeau%20have%20clashed%20publicly%2C%20but%20Trudeau%20is%20not%20one%20to%20be%20caught%20off%20guard.%20On%20Thursday%2C%20he%20revealed%20that%20his%20officials%20had%20been%20quietly%20talking%20to%20Trump's%20campaign%20team%20for%20months%2C%20readying%20for%20a%20potential%20return.%20Trudeau%20didn't%20waste%20a%20minute%E2%80%94he%20reinstated%20a%20Cabinet%20committee%20on%20US-Canada%20relations%2C%20led%20by%20Deputy%20Prime%20Minister%20Chrystia%20Freeland%2C%20to%20deal%20with%20anything%20Trump%202.0%20might%20throw%20at%20them.%20And%20he%20was%20among%20the%20first%20to%20call%20Trump%20after%20the%20win%2C%20showing%20that%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20the%20US%2C%20Trudeau%20is%20all%20about%20pragmatism%2C%20or%2C%20dare%20I%20say%2C%20even%20subservience.%20His%20office%20spelt%20it%20out%20well%3A%20%E2%80%9CFollowing%20the%20election%20of%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20for%20a%20second%20term%2C%20the%20Cabinet%20Committee%20will%20focus%20on%20critical%20Canada-US%20issues.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US-Canada%20relationship%20is%20unlike%20anything%20else%20in%20the%20world.%20The%20two%20countries%20are%20more%20like%20siblings%20rather%20than%20neighbours%2C%20no%20matter%20who%20sits%20in%20the%20Oval%20Office.%20They%20are%20two%20very%20prosperous%20countries%3A%20Canada's%20per%20capita%20income%20is%20over%20%2458%2C000%2C%20while%20America's%20is%20%2481%2C000.%20They%20have%20got%20each%20other's%20backs%20on%20defence%2C%20border%20security%2C%20and%20law%20enforcement.%20The%20overlap%20is%20everywhere%E2%80%94from%20culture%20and%20sports%20to%20leisure%20and%20shared%20traditions.%20They%20have%20much%20more%20in%20common%20between%20them%20than%20either%20of%20them%20has%20with%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConsider%20this%3A%20in%202023%2C%20the%20US-Canada%20trade%20hit%20over%20a%20trillion%20dollars%2C%20with%20%242.8%20billion%20crossing%20their%20border%20every%20single%20day.%20They%20are%20each%20other's%20biggest%20trade%20partners%2C%20with%20Canada%20sending%2078%25%20of%20its%20goods%20and%20services%20to%20the%20US%20every%20year%2C%20and%20over%20400%2C000%20people%20moving%20across%20their%20shared%205%2C525-mile%20border%20daily.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ECanada%20Has%20Five%20Eyes%20By%20Its%20Side%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELet's%20keep%20in%20mind%20that%20Canada%20is%20a%20NATO%20member%20and%20the%20countries%20in%20the%20grouping%20are%20quite%20united%20and%20usually%20back%20each%20other%20against%20any%20third%20party.%20Then%20there%20is%20the%20intelligence-sharing%20bond%20under%20the%20Five%20Eyes%20institution.%20The%20Five%20Eyes%20alliance%E2%80%94a%20formidable%20network%20comprising%20the%20US%2C%20the%20UK%2C%20Canada%2C%20Australia%2C%20and%20New%20Zealand%E2%80%94has%20been%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20global%20intelligence%20operations%20for%20decades.%20The%20alliance%20was%20built%20to%20facilitate%20intelligence%20collection%20and%20sharing%20among%20its%20members%2C%20ensuring%20a%20near-seamless%20flow%20of%20critical%20security%20information.%20In%20light%20of%20Canada's%20recent%20allegations%20against%20Indian%20officials%2C%20the%20alliance%20ought%20to%20have%20played%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20sharing%20information%20with%20Canadian%20intelligence%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20as%20a%20core%20member%20of%20the%20Five%20Eyes%2C%20Canada%20has%20access%20to%20intelligence%20and%20insights%20that%20most%20nations%20can%20only%20aspire%20to%20attain.%20If%20Canada%20believes%20it%20has%20intelligence%20linking%20Indian%20officials%20to%20Nijjar's%20assassination%2C%20it%20is%20likely%20benefiting%20from%20the%20information-sharing%20protocols%20within%20the%20Five%20Eyes%20network.%20Notably%2C%20Canada%20may%20be%20leveraging%20Five%20Eyes%20capabilities%20to%20cross-reference%20signals%20intelligence%20(SIGINT)%20and%20other%20classified%20insights%2C%20allowing%20them%20to%20build%20a%20stronger%20case%20against%20India%2C%20should%20any%20concrete%20evidence%20exist.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ELet%20Canada's%20Voters%20Decide%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnyway%2C%20India%20might%20just%20have%20to%20play%20the%20waiting%20game%20until%20Canada's%20next%20general%20election%2C%20now%20less%20than%20a%20year%20away.%20Trudeau's%20grip%20on%20power%20since%20he%20took%20office%20in%202015%20is%20looking%20shakier%20than%20ever%20today.%20If%20he%20is%20out%20of%20the%20picture%2C%20the%20new%20government's%20stance%20on%20India%20could%20breathe%20fresh%20life%20into%20those%20frosty%20bilateral%20ties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Syed%20Zubair%20Ahmed%20is%20a%20London-based%20senior%20Indian%20journalist%20with%20three%20decades%20of%20experience%20with%20the%20Western%20media)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731315780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2F58f320r_trump-canda_625x300_11_November_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Findia-or-canada-which-way-will-trump-look-6992629%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22With%20Trump's%20return%20to%20the%20Oval%20Office%20just%20weeks%20away%2C%20some%20in%20India%20are%20already%20hoping%20that%20he%20will%20put%20New%20Delhis%20new%20adversary%2C%20Canadian%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau%2C%20in%20his%20place.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Findia-or-canada-which-way-will-trump-look-6992629%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Nigerian%20Supernatural%20Thriller%20%E2%80%98Suspicion%E2%80%99%20From%20%E2%80%98Seven%E2%80%99%20Director%20Tosin%20Igho%20Lands%20at%20Prime%20Video%20(EXCLUSIVE)%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731315741000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FSuspicion.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F