2009.%C2%A0Created%20using%203D%20visualisation%20technology%2C%20it%20also%20features%20a%20large%20dragon%20tattoo%20covering%20Betty's%20stomach%20and%20chest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20house%20in%20the%20area%20has%20been%20dedicated%20entirely%20to%20Betty's%20murder%2C%20with%20large%20stickers%20on%20the%20windows%20and%20TV%20screens%20showing%20the%20crime%20scene%2C%20a%20documentary%20and%20images%20of%20the%20woman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20holographic%20has%20been%20created%20to%20reach%20out%20to%20people%2C%20who%20may%20have%20knowledge%20about%20the%20murder%20case%20but%20did%20not%20come%20forward%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20official%20statement%2C%20Benjamin%20van%20Gogh%2C%20coordinator%20of%20the%20Amsterdam%20Wanted%20and%20Missing%20Persons%20Team%2C%20noted%20that%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Bdifficult%20to%20determine%20what%20it%20takes%20to%20get%20possible%20witnesses%2C%20in%20this%20case%2C%20to%20share%20their%20information%20with%20us%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBetty's%20hologram%20may%20create%20a%20certain%20connection%20with%20her%20and%20thus%20convince%20a%20person%20to%20come%20forward.%20In%20this%20type%20of%20case%2C%20we%20always%20try%20to%20put%20a%20face%20on%20a%20victim%2C%20so%20that%20informants%20know%20who%20they're%20doing%20it%20for%2C%20and%20the%20hologram%20is%20a%20way%20of%20taking%20this%20a%20step%20further%2C%26quot%3B%20CNN%20quoted%20the%20official%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%2C%20the%20Dutch%20police%20said%20that%20Szab%C3%B3%20was%20born%20and%20brought%20up%20in%20poverty%20in%20the%20Hungarian%20city%20of%20Ny%C3%ADregyh%C3%A1za%2C%20before%20shifting%20to%20Amsterdam%20at%20the%20age%20of%2018.%20After%20landing%20in%20the%20city%2C%20she%20began%20earning%20money%20as%20a%20sex%20worker%20in%20the%20red%20light%20district.%20After%20becoming%20pregnant%2C%20she%20continued%20to%20work%20throughout%20her%20pregnancy%20and%20later%20gave%20birth%20to%20a%20son%20in%20November%202008.%20The%20child%20was%20later%20placed%20with%20a%20foster%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBetty%20was%20found%20dead%20on%20the%20night%20of%20February%2019%2C%202009%2C%20when%20two%20of%20her%20fellow%20sex%20workers%20reached%20her%20workroom%20on%20Oudezijds%20Achterburgwal.%20They%20realised%20they%20didn't%20see%20her%20or%20hear%20the%20music%20she%20usually%20played.%20At%20around%201%20AM%2C%20they%20found%20her%20body%20stabbed%20dozens%20of%20times.%20She%20was%2019%2C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fworld%2F2024%2Fnov%2F10%2Fdutch-police-use-hologram-to-try-to-solve-2009-sex-worker-killing%5C%22%3E%20The%20Guardian%20%3C%2Fa%3Ereported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20past%2015%20years%2C%20police%20carried%20out%20a%20large-scale%20investigation%20into%20the%20case%2C%20monitoring%20CCTVs%20and%20interviewing%20witnesses.%20The%20case%20remained%20unsolved.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20reward%20for%20any%20information%20related%20to%20the%20case%20has%20been%20hiked%20to%20%E2%82%AC30%2C000%20(around%20%2432%2C160).%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731315720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fscq145k8_amsterdam-sex-workers-murder_625x300_11_November_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdutch-police-use-hologram-to-solve-2009-amsterdam-sex-workers-murder-6992272%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Netherlands%20Police%20are%20using%20an%20innovative%20life-size%20hologram%20of%20a%20sex%20worker%2C%20killed%20in%20Amsterdam%20in%20February%202009%2C%20to%20uncover%20new%20information%20about%20the%20cold%20case%20and%20bring%20her%20killer%20or%20killers%20to%20justice.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdutch-police-use-hologram-to-solve-2009-amsterdam-sex-workers-murder-6992272%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D