as%2C%20%26quot%3BFind%20me%20a%20startup%20working%20in%20this%20specific%20subdomain%20with%20a%20founder%20that%20has%20experience%20at%20an%20S%26amp%3BP500%20company%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20cofounder%20and%20CTO%20Walid%20Mustapha.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20startup%20generates%20revenue%20by%20charging%20a%20license%20fee%20to%20access%20the%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20fundraising%2C%20the%20Deckmatch%20team%20had%20a%20strict%20rule%20%E2%80%94%20they%20would%20only%20accept%20investment%20from%20VCs%20who%20were%20using%20their%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDeckmatch%20said%20its%20%243.1%20million%20seed%20round%20was%20oversubscribed.%20It%20was%20led%20by%20Alliance%20VC%20and%20Luminar%20Ventures%2C%20with%20participation%20from%20First%20Degree%20Capital%20and%20Skyfall%20Ventures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20fresh%20funding%2C%20Deckmatch%20plans%20to%20double%20down%20on%20its%20research%20and%20development%20efforts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECheck%20out%20the%2013-slide%20deck%20it%20used%20to%20secure%20the%20funding.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Deckmatch%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F672ceacb88cea3ba1c1eeede%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22844%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EDeckmatch%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Deckmatch%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F672ceacb5ec9bfa3d63c5af6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22844%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EDeckmatch%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Deckmatch%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F672ceacb5ec9bfa3d63c5af7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22844%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EDeckmatch%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2