20also%20demanded%20the%20Delhi%20government%20take%20a%20decision%20on%20a%20permanent%20ban%20on%20firecrackers%20-%20the%20chemical%20residue%20of%20which%20blankets%20the%20city%20in%20cloud%20of%20toxic%20smog%20that%20smothers%20residents%20and%20severely%20endangers%20their%20health%20-%20in%20the%20city%20by%20November%2025.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday's%20hearing%20follows%20last%20week's%20reprimand%20for%20the%20Delhi%20government%20and%20police%2C%20each%20of%20which%20was%20issued%20a%20notice%20to%20explain%20to%20the%20court%20why%20they%20had%20failed%20to%20implement%20and%20enforce%20the%20ban%20on%20firecrackers%2C%20which%20is%20announced%20before%20Diwali%20every%20year%20and%20has%20little%20or%20no%20effect.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-notice-to-delhi-top-cop-for-not-implementing-firecracker-ban-6940542%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20Steps%20Taken%3F%26quot%3B%20Court%20Pulls%20Up%20Delhi%20Govt%2C%20Cops%20On%20Cracker%20Ban%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%2C%20today%20the%20Delhi%20Police%20chief%20filed%20an%20affidavit%20explaining%20steps%20taken%20but%20the%20court%20-%20which%20earlier%20pointed%20out%20it%20appears%20quite%20obvious%20the%20ban%20had%2C%20so%20far%2C%20failed%20to%20work%20-%20was%20unimpressed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20widespread%20news%20reports%20the%20ban%20on%20firecrackers%20(in%20Delhi%20NCR)%20was%20not%20implemented%20at%20all...%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said%20last%20week.%20Today%20it%20said%2C%C2%A0%26quot%3BAfter%20October%2014%20did%20the%20police%20go%20and%20stop%20sale%20of%20firecrackers%3F%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20asked%20today%2C%20to%20which%20the%20police%20said%20%26quot%3Byes%26quot%3B%20but%20was%20shot%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20all%20eyewash...%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmere-eyewash-supreme-court-raps-punjab-haryana-over-stubble-burning-6853630%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BMere%20Eyewash%26quot%3B%3A%20Court%20Raps%20Punjab%2C%20Haryana%20On%20Farm%20Fires%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20also%20complained%20the%20late%20notification%20of%20the%20ban%20had%20not%20helped%20but%2C%20again%2C%20the%20court%20was%20disinclined%20to%20offer%20sympathy%2C%20noting%2C%20%26quot%3B...%20we%20find%20that%20implementation%20of%20the%20order%20was%20not%20taken%20seriously%20by%20the%20police%20and%20there%20is%20nothing%20in%20the%20affidavit%20to%20show%20ban%20order%20was%20communicated%20to%20manufacturers%20and%20stores%20making%20and%20selling%20firecrackers%20(in%20Delhi).%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20direct%20the%20Commissioner%20of%20Police%20to%20immediately%20take%20action%20and%20inform%20all%20concerned%20about%20the%20ban...%20to%20ensure%2C%20during%20the%20ban%2C%20no%20manufacturers%20stores%20or%20sells%20firecrackers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20government%20did%20not%20escape%20the%20court's%20attention%2C%20as%20it%20was%20asked%20why%20it%20had%20delayed%20announcing%20the%20ban%20on%20firecrackers.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20quite%20possible%20that%20by%20that%20time%20(the%20ban%20was%20promulgated)%20people%20who%20burst%20firecrackers%20during%20ban%20acquired%20a%20stock%20of%20firecrackers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20Monday%20after%20Diwali%20(which%20was%20on%20November%2031)%20the%20air%20quality%20index%2C%20or%20AQI%2C%20in%20Delhi%20plummeted%20across%20the%20city%20to%20the%20'severe'%20category.%20The%20AQI%20reading%20fell%20past%20the%20400-mark%20(on%20a%20scale%20of%20500)%20in%20many%20neighbourhoods%2C%20including%20Anand%20Vihar%2C%20Rohini%2C%20Ashok%20Vihar%2C%20and%20Vivek%20Vihar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM2.5%20are%20fine%20inhalable%20particles%