hackles%20of%20bonded%20labour%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJayam%20%3Cem%3EAkka%20%3C%2Fem%3E(%E2%80%98elder%20sister%E2%80%99%20in%20Tamil%2C%20a%20term%20affectionately%20used%20by%20her%20team%20and%20community)%20was%20born%20into%20a%20family%20bound%20by%20bonded%20labour.%20She%20occasionally%20speaks%20courageously%20about%20the%20indignities%20of%20her%20early%20years%2C%20recalling%20tasks%20assigned%20to%20Dalit%20women%20and%20girls%20%E2%80%94%20including%20washing%20menstrual%20clothes%20for%20influential%20households%20where%20her%20father%20served%20as%20a%20bonded%20labourer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnwilling%20to%20continue%20a%20life%20of%20indignity%20and%20determined%20to%20break%20this%20cycle%20of%20intergenerational%20exploitation%2C%20she%20founded%20Salem%20People%20Trust%20(SPT).%20Since%202007%2C%20SPT%20has%20rescued%20and%20rehabilitated%20376%20bonded%20labourers%2C%20helped%201%2C372%20children%20return%20to%20school%20free%20from%20bonded%20labour%2C%20and%20continues%20to%20advocate%20for%20child%20rights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20our%20initial%20focus%20was%20on%20ending%20bonded%20labour%2C%20we%20are%20proud%20to%20have%20freed%20nearly%2080%20percent%20of%20those%20affected%2C%20with%20their%20children%20now%20attending%20school.%20Our%20board%20members%20and%20staff%20are%20chosen%20from%20former%20bonded%20labourers%20and%20others%20with%20lived%20experiences%2C%20including%20child%20labour%20and%20the%20pressures%20of%20sex-selective%20abortion.%20We%20believe%20those%20who%20have%20lived%20through%20these%20challenges%20are%20best%20positioned%20to%20serve%20as%20community%20organisers%20and%20leaders.%20Their%20deep%20understanding%20of%20the%20community%E2%80%99s%20struggles%20allows%20us%20to%20effectively%20address%20the%20needs%20and%20bring%20meaningful%20change%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Jayam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EEmpowering%20women%E2%80%99s%20leadership%20with%2