y.%20%E2%80%9CWe%2C%20as%20the%20district%20administration%2C%20are%20also%20supporting%20their%20efforts%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20the%20SHG%20ladies%20who%20are%20leading%20the%20initiative%2C%20and%20they%20are%20ensuring%20its%20success.%20We%E2%80%99re%20seeing%20positive%20feedback%20for%20the%20project.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20West%20Kameng%20district%20magistrate%20also%20informs%20that%20to%20address%20the%20significant%20issue%20of%20transportation%2C%20the%20administration%20and%20the%20NGO%20are%20discussing%20various%20measures%2C%20including%20a%20collaboration%20with%20the%20Indian%20Army.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201370px)%20100vw%2C%201370px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fenv-day-with-SSB-Dirang_11zon-1730809773.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221370%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20cleanup%20drive%20with%20SSB%2C%20Dirang%2C%20on%20World%20Environment%20Day%2C%20in%202023%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fenv-day-with-SSB-Dirang_11zon-1730809773.jpg%201370w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fenv-day-with-SSB-Dirang_11zon-1730809773-300x226.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fenv-day-with-SSB-Dirang_11zon-1730809773-500x376.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fenv-day-with-SSB-Dirang_11zon-1730809773-768x578.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fenv-day-with-SSB-Dirang_11zon-1730809773-150x113.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-374404%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221031%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EA%20cleanup%20drive%20with%20SSB%2C%20Dirang%2C%20on%20World%20Environment%20Day%2C%20in%202023%3C%2Ff