0often%20miss%20their%20dialysis%20sessions%2C%20leading%20to%20poor%20outcomes.%20In%20India%2C%20a%20CKD%20patient%20on%20dialysis%20lives%2C%20on%20average%2C%20for%20four%20years%2C%20while%20in%20the%20West%2C%20patients%20live%20for%20over%2015%20years.%20We%20need%20to%20improve%20outcomes%20for%20our%20country%2C%E2%80%9D%20emphasises%20Prabhat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChronic%20kidney%20disease%20(CKD)%20affects%20a%20significant%20portion%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20population%2C%20although%20the%20exact%20number%20of%20patients%20remains%20unknown.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201000px)%20100vw%2C%201000px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-2024-10-30T195140.909-1730298116.jpg%3Ffit%3D1200%252C628%26quality%3D89%26ssl%3D1%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Founders%20Prabhat%20Shrivastava%2C%20Pankaj%20Tandon%20and%20Dr%20Saurabh%20Pokhariyal%20(L-R)%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-2024-10-30T195140.909-1730298116.jpg%3Fw%3D1200%26amp%3Bquality%3D89%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-2024-10-30T195140.909-1730298116.jpg%3Fresize%3D300%252C157%26amp%3Bquality%3D89%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-2024-10-30T195140.909-1730298116.jpg%3Fresize%3D500%252C262%26amp%3Bquality%3D89%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-2024-10-30T195140.909-1730298116.jpg%3Fresize%3D768%252C402%26amp%3Bquality%3D89%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-2024-10-30T195140.909-1730298116.jpg%3Fresize%3D150%252C79%26amp%3Bquality%3D89%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-373632%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EFounders%20Prabhat%20Shrivastava%2C%20Pankaj%20Tandon%20and%20Dr%20Saurabh%20Pokhariyal%20(L-R)%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDialysis%20is%20a%20vital%20treatment%20for%20patients%20with%20kidney%20failure%2C%20filtering%20waste%20products%20and%20excess%20fluid%20from%20the%20blood%20when%20the%20kidneys%20can%20no%20longer%20function%20properly.%20This%20life-saving%20procedure%20involves%20removing%20blood%20from%20the%20body%20through%20a%20needle%2C%20passing%20it%20through%20a%20machine%20to%20filter%20out%20harmful%20substances%2C%20and%20then%20returning%20the%20clean%20blood%20to%20the%20body.%20Typically%2C%20dialysis%20becomes%20necessary%20when%20kidney%20function%20declines%20significantly%2C%20reaching%20a%20point%20where%20natural%20filtration%20is%20insufficient%20to%20support%20the%20body%E2%80%99s%20health%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Dr%20Saurabh%20Pokhariyal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229669016977%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20problem%20of%20accessibility%20remains%2C%20the%20other%20concern%20is%20affordability.%20To%20provide%20dialysis%20at%20no%20cost%2C%20the%20Pradhan%20Mantri%20National%20Dialysis%20Programme%20(PMNDP)%20was%20rolled%20out%20in%20April%202016.%20The%20programme%20has%20two%20components%3A%20Hemodialysis%20(HD)%20services%20and%20Peritoneal%20dialysis%20(PD)%20services.%20Under%20the%20PMNDP%2C%20the%20government%20has%20set%20up%201%2C530%20centres%20across%20the%20country%2C%20still%20leaving%20a%20significant%20gap.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CKey%20