gramme%20based%20on%20a%20multi-sensory%20approach.%20This%20programme%20is%20offered%20to%20the%20child%20after%20an%20assessment%20of%20his%2Fher%20strengths%20and%20needs%20using%20global%20standardised%20assessment%20tools.%20The%20remediation%20programme%20is%20offered%20for%20a%20period%20of%20one%20year%20at%20the%20minimum%20to%20two%20years%20at%20the%20maximum%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20intensity%20of%20the%20remediation%20required%2C%20after%20which%20the%20child%20is%20mainstreamed%20back%20to%20the%20regular%20school%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20website%20further%20notes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EOrigins%20of%20MDA%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Chandrasekhar%20recalls%20attending%20a%20dyslexia%20remediation%20training%20programme%20in%201992%20with%20his%20wife%20to%20help%20his%20dyslexic%20son.%20After%20the%20training%20programme%2C%20the%20participants%20met%20for%20dinner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229669016977%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%C2%A0%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20Chandrasekhar%20recalls%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20trainer%20who%20had%20come%20from%20England%2C%20Hazel%20Mckay%2C%20suggested%20that%20in%20order%20to%20undertake%20some%20serious%20action%2C%20it%20would%20be%20better%20to%20form%20an%20association%20and%20work%20together.%20Initially%2C%20the%20association%20had%20a%20group%20of%20trainees%20along%20with%20a%20few%20parents%20and%20special%20educators.%20Since%20I%20was%20personally%20involved%20in%20some%20social%20activities%20at%20that%20time%2C%20I%20volunteered%20for%20this%20good%20cause.%20We%20all%20got%20together%20and%20decided%20to%20form%20the%20MDA%2C%20and%20I%20was%20selected%20to%20be%20the%20secretary%20of%20the%20association.%E2%80%9D%3C%2