-crisis-well-digging-day-zero-zenrainman%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBiome%20Environmental%20Trust%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20launch%20India%E2%80%99s%20first%20indirect%20potable%20water%20reuse%20project.%20This%20innovative%20initiative%2C%20located%20in%20Devanahalli%2C%2040%20kilometres%20northeast%20of%20Bengaluru%2C%20uses%20managed%20aquifer%20recharge%20to%20achieve%20sustainable%20water%20reuse.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20participants%20%5Bof%20this%20project%5D%2C%20the%20project%20produces%206.4%20lakh%20litres%20of%20potable%20drinking%20water%20per%20day%2C%20adhering%20to%20BIS%20(Bureau%20of%20Indian%20Standards)-10500%20standards.%20The%20clean%20water%20directly%20benefits%20thousands%20of%20residents%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F139499%2Fdevanahalli-toilets-karnataka-odf-fstp-swachh-bharat%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDevanahalli%20%3C%2Fa%3Emunicipality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20does%20this%20work%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%222400846096%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimply%20put%2C%20treated%20wastewater%20from%20a%20sewage%20treatment%20plant%20is%20first%20pumped%20into%20Bagalur%20Lake%2C%20where%20it%20is%20diluted%20with%20rainwater.%20This%20water%20is%20then%20directed%20to%20Devanahalli%E2%80%99s%20Sihineeru%20Kere%20Lake%20through%20a%20pipeline%2C%20further%20diluted%20with%20rainwater%2C%20and%20subsequently%20filtered%20through%20the%20earth%20to%20recharge%20the%20aquifer.%20The%20water%20is%20then%20picked%20up%20from%20the%20aquifer%20through%20a%20dug%20well%20and%20shallow%20filter%20borewells%2C%20treated%2C%20and%20then%20supplied%20to%20the%20town%20residents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhy%20is%20this%20an%20indirect%20potable%20water%20reuse%20project%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20project%20uses%20an%20environmental%20buffer%20like%20a%20lake%20for%20dilution%20with%20rainwater%20and%2For%20a%20groundwater%20aquifer%20for%20earth%20filtration.%20This%20water%20eventually%20goes%20through%20a%20final%20treatment%20stage%20before%20it%20is%20supplied%20to%20residents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229253875046%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%E2%80%99s%20more%2C%20the%20project%20is%20part%20of%20a%20larger%20effort%20to%20rejuvenate%2065%20lakes%20in%20Bengaluru%20employing%20treated%20wastewater%20and%20rainwater.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20project%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20involves%20reviving%20an%20old%20well%20and%20digging%20borewells%20to%20access%20the%20aquifer%2C%20along%20with%20the%20installation%20of%20water%20treatment%20plants%20in%20two%20phases.%20Now%2C%20the%20system%20provides%206.4%20lakh%20litres%20of%20water%20daily%2C%20helping%20supplement%20the%20domestic%20water%20requirement%20of%2045%2C000%20residents%20in%20Devanahalli.%20This%20was%20made%20possible%20through%20the%20collaboration%20of%20many%20organisations%20%E2%80%94%20including%20Carl%20Zeiss%2C%20Rotary%20South%20Parade%20Bangalore%2C%20and%20Wipro%20Foundation.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201000px)%20100vw%2C%201000px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWater-Reuse-Project-Lake-Image-1730296908.jpg%3Ffit%3D1200%252C628%26quality%3D89%26ssl%3D1%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bengaluru%20water%20crisis%20and%20lake%20rejuvenation%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetteri